      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-characteristic/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "八个顶点，十二条棱，六个面，看似毫无关联。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-characteristic",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-characteristic/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "但欧拉发现，它们之间藏着一个惊人的恒等关系。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-characteristic",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "formula-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-characteristic/yunxi/formula-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "把顶点数减去棱数，再加上面数，记作 V 减 E 加 F。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-characteristic",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "formula-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euler-characteristic/yunxi/formula-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "立方体是 8 减 12 加 6，结果正好等于 2。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euler-characteristic",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
